<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="PN243-intro">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. toṭittalai viḻuttaṇṭiṉār pāṭiyatu.
      ituvumatu – avaṉait <app><lem wit="#C8">toṭittalai viḻuttaṇṭiṉār</lem><rdg wit="#C2 #C3">toṭitta<gap quantity="10" unit="character"/></rdg></app>
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PN243">
<l>iṉiniṉain tirakka mākiṉṟu tiṇimaṇaṟ</l>
<l>ceyvuṟu pāvaikkuk koypūt taiit</l>
<l>taṇkaya māṭu makaḷiroṭu kaipiṇaintu</l>
<l>taḻuvuvaḻit taḻīit tūṅkuvaḻit tūṅki</l>
<l>maṟaiyeṉa laṟiyā māyami lāyamō</l>
<l>ṭuyarciṉai marutat tuṟaiyuṟat tāḻntu</l>
<l>nīrnaṇip paṭikō ṭēṟic cīrmikak</l>
<l>karaiyavar maruḷat tiraiyakam pitira</l>
<l>neṭunīrk kuṭṭattut tuṭumeṉap pāyntu</l>
<l>kuḷittumaṇaṟ koṇṭa kallā viḷamai</l>
<l>yaḷitō tāṉē yāṇṭuṇṭu kollō</l>
<l>toṭittalai viḻuttaṇ ṭūṉṟi naṭukkuṟ</l>
<l>ṟirumiṭai miṭainta cilacoṟ</l>
<l>perumū tāḷarē mākiya vemakkē.</l></lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l corresp="1a-c">Thinking now it has become regret. </l>
<l corresp="10cd">Untaught youth when </l>
<l corresp="3">entwining hands with girls that play in the cool pond, </l>
<l corresp="1d-2">knitting flowers plucked for dolls that have motion, in the firm sand </l>
<l corresp="4">embracing the way one embraces, swaying the way one sways, </l>
<l corresp="5">together with companions without deception who do not know of saying “secret”, </l>
<l corresp="6">dangling from the high-branched Myrobalan tree to have the ghat, </l>
<l corresp="7">rising on mounds [of sand] settling near the water, </l>
<l corresp="9">jumping with a splash into the expanse of long water, </l>
<l corresp="7d-8">so that spray came up from the waves to confound those on the shore mightily, </l>
<l corresp="10">	[we] took the sand after bathing, </l>
<l corresp="11">– pitiful is it. Where is it, </l>
<l corresp="14">for us who have become great old men </l>
<l corresp="13">of few words posed at long intervals, </l>
<l corresp="12">trembling, leaning on excellent sticks with ringed heads? </l>
</lg>
    </div>
